KitItem is a KeyField

	Representation
		Group Fields
			Company				is an InventoryCompany
			InventoryLocation
			Item

	Ontology
		business class is KitItem
		Context
			ItemGroup

	Field Rules
		Company
			if (InventoryLocation entered)
				required
					"CompanyIsRequiredWhenLocationIsEntered"
			constraint (ItemGroup = Company.ItemGroup)
				"CompanyDoesNotBelongToThisItemGroup"

		InventoryLocation
			if (Company entered)
				required
					"LocationIsRequiredWhenCompanyIsEntered"
				

